<body>
<div><head>喪服要集</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.2">宗譜<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.3">始封之君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.4">別子一人為祖。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.5">杜佑《通典》卷七十三傳純問賀循要記云云，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.6">引杜氏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.7">循其文義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.8">宜為此篇之首，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-1a.9">據補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.2">別子者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.3">君嫡妻之子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.4">長子之母弟也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.5">君命為祖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.6">其子則為大宗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.7">常有一主，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.8">審昭穆之序，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.9">辨親疏之別，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.10">是故百代不遷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.11">若無子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.12">則支子為後。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.13">雖七十，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.14">無無主婦。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.15">若殤死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.16">則縗絰加一等，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.17">以兄弟之列代之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.18">殤無為父道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.19">兄弟昭穆同故也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.20">死皆為之𪗋縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.21">其月數各隨親疏為限；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.22">雖尊、雖出嫁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.23">猶不敢降也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.24">屬絕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.25">則為之𪗋縗三月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.26">若始封君相傳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.27">則自祖始封君。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.28">其支子孫皆宗大宗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.29">然則繼體為宗中之尊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.30">支庶莫敢宗之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.31">是以命別子為宗主，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.32">一宗奉之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.33">故曰祖者高祖也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.34">言屬逮於君則就君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.35">屬絕於君則適宗子家也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.36">而說者或云「君代代得立大宗」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.37">或云「別子之母弟亦得為祖」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.38">或云「命妾子為別子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.39">其適妻子則遷宗於君」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.40">皆非也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.41">別子之弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.42">子孫無貴賤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.43">皆宜宗別子之子孫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.44">小宗一家之長也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.45">同族則宗之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.46">其服隨親疏為比；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.47">姊妹出嫁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.48">不敢降之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.49">五屬斷服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.50">則不宗之矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.51">《通典》卷七十三引杜元凱《宗譜要集》篇目可考者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.52">僅此錄於卷首，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-2a.53">其他佚文散列於後。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.2">始死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.3">葬銘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.4">凡卿大夫士各以其官，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.5">婦人則以姓行。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.6">虞世南《北堂書鈔》卷九十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.7">凡挽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.8">天子六綍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.9">諸侯四，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.10">大夫二，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.11">士一。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-3a.12">徐堅《初學記》卷十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.2">「九仞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.3">旒委地。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.4">遺車易以轝床。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.5">舉奠祭之具及器藏物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.6">皆覆以白練。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.7">《通典》卷七十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.8">「諸侯建大旂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.9">杠七仞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.10">斿至地。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.11">畫熊虎龍文曰旂也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-4a.12">《通典》卷八十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.2">「卿建旃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.3">六斿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.4">至軫。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.5">孤卿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.6">次三公也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.7">通帛為旃，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.8">謂純赤也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.9">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.10">天子諸侯雖卒哭除服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.11">其練祥日必有位矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-5a.12">《通典》卷八十二博士許翰議引杜元凱。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.2">「父在為母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.3">冠縗裳絰帶皆疏縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.4">疏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.5">麤也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.6">《通典》卷八十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.7">三年者始死之制，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.8">如不杖周。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-6a.9">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.2">二十五月大祥祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.3">主人夕為期。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.4">朝服縞冠訖祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.5">而受布深衣十五升。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.6">外無哭者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.7">謂哀至入即位而哭也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.8">《通典》卷八十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.9">削杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.10">圓削之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.11">象竹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.12">取其便也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.13">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-7a.14">「削杖」二字據《通典》補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.2">若父母同日卒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.3">其葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.4">先母後父，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.5">皆服斬縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.6">其虞祔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.7">先父後母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.8">其服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.9">卒事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.10">反服父服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.11">若父巳葬而母卒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.12">則服母之服；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.13">至虞訖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.14">反服；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.15">既練，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.16">則服母之服；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.17">喪可除則服父之服以除之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.18">訖而服母之服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-8a.19">《通典》卷九十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.2">自天子諸侯以下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.3">若赴時速葬則赴虞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.4">至平坐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.5">必須其哀殺也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.6">若過時不葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.7">則以麻終喪而除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.8">至葬復修服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.9">既祔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.10">明一月練而祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.11">又明一月大祥而祭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.12">必再祭者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.13">象本當再歲故也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.14">若二十五月而葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.15">則便祥除不復練也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1082_CHANT_001-9a.16">《通典》卷一百二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
